<p>Bang, bang! Nothing personal, just business - this is the credo of all successful entrepreneurs. The first business began to emerge at a time, when a man climbed down from the tree or, to be more precise, when he began to use his brain. In 21st century business has reached its peak - now we have IT business! And you, yes, yes, YOU have a great chance to find out what IT business is and how this whole thing works. During this course we are going to tell you everything you might need to make your own IT business.</p>

<p>When we say "IT business", we mean the whole process: from StarUPs to huge IT corporations. You'll discover the ways to start your own IT-business, secrets of its successful growth and other useful tips&tricks. And for sure you'll meet successful startupers that share their stories and tips with you.</p>

<p>So! If you are brave enough to expand your knowledge, to find out how to become successful in IT business, to meet new friends, see all the beauty of blooming spring Kyiv and to feel true Ukrainian hospitality - WE ARE WAITING FOR YOU!!!</p>

